                    <p class="c-para">
                        Softlink develops innovative and superior technology products and solutions for customers in the international logistics and trade services. We focus on Simplifying Operations of our customers for nearly two decades by developing software products to meet their challenges.
                    </p>
                    <p class="c-para">
                        Softlink Global established in 1998 headquarter in India with region headquarter in US and Euope. Our global operation handled by more than 150+ highly experience employee along with 15 partners across 15 region and global location in the world. Today we serve more than 60,000 satisfied users in 3,500 Logistics companies. Our deep domain expertise and experience in international logistics and trade services, combined with strong technological know-how go towards creating truly winning software solutions.
                    </p>
                    <p class="c-para">
                        Our flagship products are renowned for their simplicity of use, leading-edge technology, and reduced total cost of ownership. Our client portfolio includes companies ranging from single office SME’s to large multinational companies.  Logistics service providers experience a true boost in productivity and operational efficiency through the use of our products. Our domain expertise ensures that our products deliver enhanced management control, revenue realization and accurate international trade documentation.
                    </p>
                    <p class="c-para">
                        We work together with our customers to leverage technology to automate operations, starting from consulting, to actually developing the applications. The range of services includes software development, maintenance, conversion, migration and application enhancement.
                    </p>

